  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5a7cdf62788fdd0014b59d6b",
      "text": "多角形のたとえ話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133110,
      "updated": 1518133110
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7cdf85aff09e0000c36c60",
      "text": "[多角形のたとえ話 http://ncase.me/polygons-ja/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133125,
      "updated": 1518133340
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce05eaff09e0000c36c62",
      "text": "トーマス・シェリング  [Dynamic Models of Segregation https://www.stat.berkeley.edu/~aldous/157/Papers/Schelling_Seg_Models.pdf]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133342,
      "updated": 1518134296
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce0d9aff09e0000c36c63",
      "text": " 2種類の人種がいる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133465,
      "updated": 1518133474
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce0deaff09e0000c36c64",
      "text": " 自分の周囲8マスの自分と同じ形の割合が一定以上一定以下の範囲に収まらない場合、不満を感じてランダムに引っ越す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133470,
      "updated": 1518133555
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce12faff09e0000c36c65",
      "text": " [人種隔離]状態が発生する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133552,
      "updated": 1518151081
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce1faaff09e0000c36c66",
      "text": " 意外と低い閾値で発生する、同種比率33%未満で引っ越す場合でも。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133754,
      "updated": 1518133890
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce22baff09e0000c36c67",
      "text": "  「自分が多数派で居たい」はかなり強いことがわかる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133803,
      "updated": 1518133821
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce23caff09e0000c36c68",
      "text": " まったく差別がなくても現状の隔離状態は維持される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133821,
      "updated": 1518134088
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce2c6aff09e0000c36c69",
      "text": " 逆に同種比率80%以上で引っ越す、という「積極的に[多様性]を求める態度」を設定した場合は、隔離状態が減っていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133959,
      "updated": 1518151078
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce4d4aff09e0000c36c6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518134485,
      "updated": 1518134485
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7ce05eaff09e0000c36c61",
      "text": " 同じ会社の人でまとまるとどんどん分離されていくという形で[知識獲得戦略]に絡んでくる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1518133342,
      "updated": 1518134517
    },
    {
